		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hey, that's pretty cool.
<br />
<br />Another technique I used once was stringing together a bunch of small samples by using the DMC IRQ to trigger the next one.  Doesn't seem to be done much.  That's how my speech synth worked, with 16kB of DPCM samples.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
